{"tid":1045374,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[貓蚤] 點搞好 涼又沖過 梳又梳過好似都無咩改善","createTime":"2019-03-03T14:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T03:24:37.000Z","uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9744f34b192589b74db77addfd4505f57ba54a","tid":1045374,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"貓2.5個月大到<br />\n<br />\n本身係藥房鋪生出黎領養既 <br />\n<br />\n而家大過左D就幫佢沖涼 已經沖過2次<br />\n<br />\n尋日沖涼+梳掃左2x隻 (本身睇佢身郁黎郁去得3隻到 , 無諗有咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n諗住kill左咁多會好轉<br />\n<br />\n點知d蚤好似仲活躍過之前 而家拎隻貓睇已經又見到幾隻郁緊 仲好易就跌出黎<br />\n<br />\n岩岩一郁2隻好似仲有粒蛋連住既<br />\n<br />\n點搞好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環境我更加唔敢諗會唔會跌到d蚤蛋周圍係"},{"pid":"cc863afeb256c00f81477789e86e0cbdd3d5270f","tid":1045374,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:17:58.000Z","msg":"用蚤藥水係咪唔係即死 ? 會唔會周圍都係屍 定都係要幫佢梳先會梳到出黎?"},{"pid":"aede9bcfc4b5b082b2e8d482c53b376ff0202244","tid":1045374,"uid":7854,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/221840_406c87cefc86fcab5f84a6105e141d83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F221840_406c87cefc86fcab5f84a6105e141d83.png&h=095d0b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己都俾蚤咬左3啖已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511b32573cbaed708c6fb70e8e3bf9a7fe7f0746","tid":1045374,"uid":158960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"要落藥 滴耳仔 後頸 就咁洗無用㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6eeb4dc7d15d5c6f032d5669a7b67167cce52d","tid":1045374,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"