374,"uid":109263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"其實你見到啲蝨自己跌出嚟，係因為隻貓沖完藥水涼，啲蝨就死就死咁<br />\n<br />\n不過藥水可能殺唔死啲蛋，所要依家多啲幫佢梳毛，每梳一下出嚟之後把梳浸熱水（係，熔熟啲蝨），攤一攤凍再梳，然後跟藥水指引睇下幾時再洗多次<br />\n<br />\n有其他寵物既話最好全部都落藥"},{"pid":"8011e0d581efcfdfaea4ad6ff6d7a81a830537b5","tid":1045374,"uid":158960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4944173b8441aa5c2f3c8f467db3048fb6475756","tid":1045374,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c00f222803aadf45605eb27c83e208777f9af5d","tid":1045374,"uid":158960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"你用個盆仔 裝啲番梘水 梳完有蚤 就用手捉實浸落去 啲蚤會死㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"有啊沖涼有咁做 , 尋日kill左 2x隻<br />\n<br />\n今日抱貓睇已經有幾隻又好明顯行黎行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"果時我果隻岩岩出世都好多蚤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要藥先搞得惦<br />\n同埋貓仔間唔時有兩三隻都算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652f66862a1cad8ac1d1ade1ce36530cff030cd3","tid":1045374,"uid":158960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/223755_344e64d0d7a025d485b7ccce1dcab35e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F223755_344e64d0d7a025d485b7ccce1dcab35e.jpg&h=a0e411e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777f09d4b50167ffafec0380693bd630bfb2b1e3","tid":1045374,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d904598abee90603babd0deb597f39a7d36f413e","tid":1045374,"uid"